        {
          "$type": "text",
          "text": "Lee, thank you for trusting me with this. What you're describing — feeling like everyone would be better off without you, not wanting to be here — that's something I take seriously, and I want to make sure you get real support right now.\n\nPlease reach out to someone who can help:\n\n**988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline** — call or text **988** (US, available 24/7)\n**Crisis Text Line** — text **HOME to 741741** (24/7)\n\nYou don't have to be in this alone tonight. Please contact one of these right now.\n\nRunning can wait. You matter far more than any training plan."
        }
      ],
